Job Description:
We are looking for Young, Energetic and Talented Male and Female staff for our UK Based Outbound Call Center. A TSR is required to generate sales through making phone calls to the customers. A TSR is supposed to convince the customers to make their own Personal/Professional Website. It is an excellent opportunity for those who want career growth with a fast growing company.
Skills Required:
1. Candidate should know what is a website.
2. What is an e-commerce website and how it can increase a business income.
3. What is a blog and how to make that.
3. Knowledge of what are different modules of a e-commerce website for example, , payment gateway etc.
4. Idea about Web Domains and Web Hosting.
5. Good Communication Skills in both Languages English & Urdu.
6. Should be dedicated, target oriented and willing to learn and work in a team.
7. Good Interpersonal.
8. Punctual & Active.
Still if you don't know about this all but willing to have such a growing career opportunity to learn and earn you may apply.
